headline: Coinbase Owns 'Institutional Trust' in Crypto—But 3 Public Rivals Are About To Test That Claim
summary: Coinbase Global Inc. (NASDAQ:COIN) delivered another earnings beat last week, riding a wave of crypto enthusiasm that’s pushed the market to $3.7 trillion. But as rival exchanges line up for their own public debuts and regulatory fog lifts across the industry, analysts say the company’s dominance is facing its most serious challenge yet.
